01:16:31.120 --> 01:17:57.461
Some things you just can't say out loud. I can't even give it words in English.

01:17:57.462 --> 01:18:14.986
It looks like beautiful yellows and all kinds of colors, almost like a galaxy.

01:18:14.988 --> 01:18:29.153
I saw new grass and new land features. I saw the people coming out of what looked like a fraidy hole.

01:18:29.154 --> 01:18:42.196
The people come up in this new land, and it was green, like the Garden of Eden all over again.

01:18:42.197 --> 01:18:52.435
Everything was alive. The trees were like what I've seen of the Garden of Eden.

01:18:52.436 --> 01:19:24.139
Everything was new. There was no pollution; all of it was brand new and happened in a moment.

01:19:24.140 --> 01:19:42.478
It came out of the Spirit and transformed everything with just a word.

01:19:42.479 --> 01:20:01.492
He said, 'Behold, I make all things new.'The fields were fresh, and the sky was full of light with no darkness.

01:20:01.493 --> 01:20:09.909
The canopy above the earth—the atmosphere—looked like beautiful colors.

01:20:09.910 --> 01:20:36.343
I saw pinks and yellows. Everything changed instantaneously.

01:20:36.344 --> 01:20:43.829
I was looking in, and it was moving like a movie screen. Everything was coming so fast.

01:20:43.830 --> 01:20:54.590
I could see wars and plans, and all of a sudden, humanity stopped.

01:20:54.591 --> 01:21:15.043
Everything was made new. We, the Body—the Bride—were here. Everything was fresh, like a New Heaven and a New Earth.

01:21:15.044 --> 01:21:23.718
Everything we have ever known is about to change for that thousand-year reign.

01:21:23.719 --> 01:21:32.799
I saw a glimpse of it again. It doesn't happen very often, but I want to camp there.

01:21:32.800 --> 01:21:56.638
When I try to describe it in words, I can't. It is beautiful. I feel His fire all over me.

01:21:56.639 --> 01:22:18.559
Oh, what He has so much in store for us for a thousand years. People better get excited about it.

01:22:18.560 --> 01:22:31.140
I can't explain to you how green everything was. The grass, the trees, and the bushes—there was no death.

01:22:31.141 --> 01:22:35.196
There was no death. You know how you see a dead limb here and there?

01:22:35.197 --> 01:22:42.638
Outside, you go outside and there's a dead tree limb. There was no death.

01:22:42.639 --> 01:22:51.856
There were no dead brown leaves. Everything is alive and green.

01:22:51.858 --> 01:23:05.872
The sky is alive. The very atmosphere is alive. And even the grass was perfect.

01:23:05.873 --> 01:23:15.439
It was green, but it's thick, almost like you see that old Easter basket grass. I don't know how else to describe it to you.

01:23:15.440 --> 01:23:32.013
Like you'd see moss on trees, it's so thick, like you could breathe it in, eat it, or drink it like the grass.

01:23:32.014 --> 01:23:41.657
Everything is so alive. I could just look into it, but I was pulled back and I looked over here and I could see it.

01:23:41.658 --> 01:23:53.833
As far as I could see, it was new and beautiful with pinks and yellows, and the sky was so alive.

01:23:53.834 --> 01:24:01.355
It happened as a swirl above the atmosphere, like a portal opened up.

01:24:01.356 --> 01:24:11.889
All of a sudden this portal was turning, and all of a sudden all this newness just came out of it and it just transferred everything.

01:24:11.890 --> 01:24:17.444
The portal was open and I could see it was like the size of a galaxy.

01:24:17.445 --> 01:24:23.519
It was massive. All of a sudden I saw this blue dot that looked like an Earth.

01:24:23.520 --> 01:24:30.158
It came out of it, and I thought it was an atom—like an atom or particles.

01:24:30.159 --> 01:24:49.331
That's what I thought I was looking at. But it was something new.

01:24:49.332 --> 01:24:59.274
As I was praying to the King and all these other things, I could see a scorpion's tail; I saw a scorpion.

01:24:59.275 --> 01:25:05.593
It was a part of that. All of a sudden, I kept going and going, like I was going faster and faster.

01:25:05.595 --> 01:25:15.228
I could see the King of England, and I could see there was so much demonic attached to that with the Illuminati and things like that.

01:25:15.229 --> 01:25:20.958
I was in the spirit and I could see it, and it was pulling me. I could see all the darkness in Europe.

01:25:20.959 --> 01:25:27.069
All of a sudden, I could see the agendas of China and all this stuff going on, and the war.

01:25:27.070 --> 01:25:38.619
I saw a major war break out in America. I pray and hope this is not now; this is the tribulation.

01:25:38.620 --> 01:25:51.506
I'm talking about a desolate, bad war from coast to coast. I saw Hawaii wiped out.

01:25:51.507 --> 01:25:58.488
Bad war. I saw volcanoes that were bigger in Hawaii going off all at the same time.

01:25:58.489 --> 01:26:08.734
Hell on earth all around, dead fish. It looked so scary. Then all of a sudden, everything changed.

01:26:08.735 --> 01:26:19.512
It was like peace. It came out of great turmoil, the Great Tribulation.

01:26:19.513 --> 01:26:42.319
I'm surely not looking into it right now. Glory to God, y'all. I was not expecting that today.

01:26:42.320 --> 01:26:53.396
I know I try to explain the best I can what the Holy Spirit is showing me, but some of it I just can't say with words.

01:26:53.398 --> 01:27:06.844
I do my best, but I assure you some things are just so holy you don't want to talk about them.

01:27:06.845 --> 01:27:15.907
You just say, 'Wow, Lord.'I know it may not make a whole lot of sense, some of the things I just said.

01:27:15.908 --> 01:27:32.944
You might ask, 'What is wrong with you?'because I see it. The scorpion was stinging out.

01:27:32.945 --> 01:28:04.799
Glory to God. Thank you, Lord. Thank you, Father. All I know is that You're coming soon.

01:28:04.800 --> 01:28:09.194
Father, I thank You, Lord, that we come up higher with the fire.

01:28:09.195 --> 01:28:38.843
We come out of Your throne, we come into the throne. Glory to God. Well, praise the Lord. He's worthy to be praised.

01:28:38.844 --> 01:29:03.439
I feel the anointing so strong on my face and my body right now; the weight of the glory is on me.

01:29:03.440 --> 01:29:22.569
Oh, what He does to this little prayer channel. I'm in awe of Him on a public platform.

01:29:22.570 --> 01:29:54.862
He brings our own personal things in public. Glory to God. Oh Lord, You're worthy.

01:29:54.863 --> 01:30:08.506
I can't wait. It's going to be so awesome. It's coming so soon.

01:30:08.507 --> 01:30:17.665
Most people look at it as being far out there, but when I was looking then, it looked like it could be tomorrow—like the tribulation.

01:30:17.666 --> 01:30:25.651
I saw the rider and the horse of war, the pale horse, and the dark black horse riding.

01:30:25.652 --> 01:30:41.242
They were back to back with each other, all three. The tribulation was getting ready to kick off.

01:30:41.243 --> 01:30:55.984
Glory to God. War, war, war. It's nuts. I was still trying to look at China and all that, and that dragon came up out of that volcano.

01:30:55.985 --> 01:31:17.322
I saw a massive volcano going off in, I believe it was Japan. It was a massive volcano, and lava was going down it like Pompeii.

01:31:17.323 --> 01:31:28.269
That lava was coming out of that thing, causing great destruction.

01:31:28.270 --> 01:31:35.537
Well, praise the Lord, y'all. Thank you for joining me. He saw Yosemite.

01:31:35.538 --> 01:31:44.070
Yeah, Yosemite. I heard Yosemite, but I didn't see it. I heard it. He was praying over Yosemite National Park.

01:31:44.071 --> 01:31:53.308
I could hear something and there was rumbling, and he said, 'Yosemite.'I thought, 'What?'Then I remembered more.

01:31:53.309 --> 01:32:01.839
I pray because when I'm hearing in the spirit and trying to decipher what I'm hearing, I realize that's America, California.

01:32:01.840 --> 01:32:14.079
Yosemite has waterfalls. I didn't know where it was. There are mountains there; I think it's the Sierra Mountains.

01:32:14.080 --> 01:32:23.681
I think I looked it up while you were praying. Well, if I lived next to Yosemite, I'd really pray hard for what I just saw.

01:32:23.682 --> 01:32:38.057
Oh goodness. None of that is this. That's why I said, 'Is this tribulation?'But we have time.

01:32:38.058 --> 01:32:47.715
Boy, if you get Jesus Christ to be your Lord and personal Savior and you surrender to Him today, you don't have to go through the tribulation.

01:32:47.716 --> 01:33:01.078
It's not meant for us. Again, the body was not here. We are not appointed under wrath, ladies and gentlemen; we're appointed under grace.

01:33:01.079 --> 01:33:07.112
I'm telling you, as the Body of Christ, it's time to rise up because our redemption is drawn nigh.

01:33:07.113 --> 01:33:23.310
I don't want to be here for that, for another glimpse into it—the elements, the earthquakes, the volcanoes, the pestilence, the plague, the war, the antichrist.

01:33:23.311 --> 01:33:38.471
I mean, folks, it's awful. People ask, 'Will people live through it?'No, it's beyond the elements, the pestilence, and the wars.

01:33:38.472 --> 01:33:47.630
It will be very hard to live through the tribulation. People are just going to die; they're going to be dead all over the place.

01:33:47.631 --> 01:34:00.938
It's absolute hell on earth for seven years. So many in the Body of Christ believe that we go through that.

01:34:00.939 --> 01:34:10.843
How foolish. God is not a wife beater. He does not beat His bride.

01:34:10.844 --> 01:34:30.176
People look at Him and say, 'Well, we're going to go through that because of whatever they think they find in the scripture.'I'm telling you that we are not here for the tribulation—the remnant, the people, His bride, the ones that have their lamps full of oil.

01:34:30.177 --> 01:34:38.229
God has His hand on us and He's going to take us out of this. They say, 'Where is that in the Word?'It's all through the Word.

01:34:38.230 --> 01:34:45.714
But I'm not here to argue with you about it. I stay ready. Glory to God.

01:34:45.715 --> 01:34:59.226
Well, I pray this video blessed you all today. It blessed me. I will take that in my memory bank for the rest of my life.

01:34:59.227 --> 01:35:17.198
If the Lord tarries and I don't see the rapture, I believe we're about to see something.

01:35:17.199 --> 01:35:26.097
Well, we pray it. Like I said, this video blesses you. I don't even know how to end it other than just tell you all we love you.

01:35:26.098 --> 01:35:31.885
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

01:35:31.886 --> 01:35:38.533
Thank you for entering into our prayer time with us. We appreciate you praying with us.

01:35:38.534 --> 01:35:48.098
We pray you got refreshed and that the Holy Spirit becomes more real to you as you walk out your relationship with Him.

01:35:48.099 --> 01:36:05.830
From glory to glory, He's changing you. Remember that Jesus loves you and we love you. God bless you all and we'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

